{"tid":1596121,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Moko 間丸十あぶり牧場真是好撚正","createTime":"2019-09-26T11:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:59:01.000Z","uid":247465,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9578835dced0aeb69059100674735e4de01e4d4a","tid":1596121,"uid":247465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"話說想食燒肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n約左女朋友就去左moko<br />\n見到間 叫 丸十あぶり牧場<br />\n好似見到環境幾好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到去叫左<br />\n<br />\n和牛拼盤（20塊牛，$580）<br />\n蔬菜烏冬（80蚊）<br />\n和牛三文治 （$125）<br />\n<br />\nDLLM 樣樣難食到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和牛拼盤d 牛深啡色，勁唔新鮮成陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ri0fNP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fri0fNP5.jpg&h=449d5285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10件嘔返4件出黎<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dif7DWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDif7DWR.jpg&h=d492f42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳥冬用d 急凍蔬菜烏冬加味精湯上<br />\n和牛三文治完全冇肉味 以為自己食緊吞拿魚三文治<br />\n埋單1000 我真是diu 出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後勸大家唔好再幫襯d 連鎖鋪<br />\n真是間間都又垃圾又貴<br />\n食親都失望<br />\n真是幫襯d 黃的小店好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問平時一個人食都follow 黃藍商店名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次睇少次都中伏<br />\n你唔係賤到俾錢d 地產商或大集團食垃圾啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇啲黃的燒肉店推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2d37d00dc0d26bb